# Testing

## Organization

- Unit: `test/unit/` mirrors `src/` — `.test.ts` / `.test.tsx`
- E2E: `test/e2e/` — `.spec.ts`

## Practices

- Test user-facing behavior, not implementation details
- Use `getByRole`, `getByLabelText` (accessibility-first queries)
- Mock external APIs and third-party libraries
- Mock `next/navigation` hooks (`usePathname`, `useRouter`)
- Mock `ThemeProvider` when components depend on theme
- E2E: test keyboard navigation, focus management, ARIA labels/roles
